    <div class="w-[333.22px] h-[102px] left-0 top-[65px] absolute text-stone-500 text-sm font-normal leading-[27px]">As my time in New York City draws to a close in the coming months, I find myself reflecting on my time in the concrete jungle. It certainly was not an easy time, but it was one hell of a ride.</div>
    <div class="w-[351px] h-32 left-0 top-[198px] absolute border-l-2 border-neutral-200">
