    <div class="w-[228.01px] h-[21px] left-0 top-[761px] absolute text-stone-500 text-sm font-normal leading-[27px]">Then of course, my luck ran out.</div>
    <div class="w-[340.25px] h-[75px] left-0 top-[816px] absolute text-stone-500 text-[15px] font-normal leading-[27px]">To start off the new decade I visited family back home in Colorado. We went to the slopes and I fell off a ski lift and shattered my knee.</div>
    <div class="w-[334.11px] h-[75px] left-0 top-[925px] absolute text-stone-500 text-base font-normal leading-[27px]">So now I head back to the city, limping on crutches, in one of the fastest paced places on earth. Just my luck.</div>
    <div class="w-[350.17px] h-[156px] left-0 top-[1034px] absolute text-stone-500 text-[15px] font-normal leading-[27px]">It started out as a quiet panic amongst my wife and her family. Being from China, her parents had family back home and were monitoring the situation in Wuhan closely. I scoffed off concerns at first. After all, it was way over there. It could never happen here....right?</div>
    <div class="w-[210.48px] h-[21px] left-0 top-[1224px] absolute text-stone-500 text-sm font-normal leading-[27px]">But it did, and it swept in fast.</div>
